</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="signals.html">Home</a> &rarr; Cookie Policy</div>
  <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
<p class="updated">Last updated: February 2026</p>

<h2>1. What Are Cookies</h2>
<p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help the site function and provide usage information.</p>

<h2>2. Essential Cookies</h2>
<p>These are required for the Service to function: authentication tokens, session identifiers, and security tokens. You cannot opt out of essential cookies.</p>

<h2>3. Analytics Cookies</h2>
<p>We use anonymized analytics to understand how visitors use AgoraIQ Signals. These are optional and can be declined.</p>

<h2>4. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
<p>Stripe may set cookies for payment processing. No advertising cookies are used.</p>

<h2>5. Managing Cookies</h2>
<p>You can control cookies through your browser settings. Blocking essential cookies may prevent the Service from functioning correctly.</p>

<h2>6. Contact</h2>
<p>Questions: <a href="mailto:legal@agoraiq.net">legal@agoraiq.net</a></p>
</div>
